divs: sighting detailswas playing golf. i sighted ufo above and in the distance, yet appeared not too far. pointed it out to my golf partner, who also did not understand what were were looking at. appeared to be two or three rectangular gray\black parachutes conntected. hovered and appeared to be coming toward us, but very slowly as decended. we could not figure out what we were looking at as it was soon apparent this was not any type of parachute. however, there did seem to be some type of ropes\appendages holding the two or three rectangules together. they floated, or seemed to, towards us for a few minutes. we played the hole and drove down to the green. i saw them just before driving down the hill, and in the next second they were gone from the sky with no sign of anything at all. the sky was clear and very open. it couldn't have disappeared that fast as big as it was without still being in view in such a short time.
